      还差
      %span.orange= @project.rate - user_correct_count % @project.rate
      题就可以独立助捐
      %span.orange= (user_correct_count/@project.rate + 1) * @project.benefit.unit_rate
      #{@project.benefit.unit}#{@project.benefit.short_name}。
